  "title": "Identification of a nonnodulating spontaneous mutant in chickpea",
  "abstract": "A non-nodulating mutant plant was discovered in the accession ICC435. Its seeds produced plants that failed to form nodules when inoculated with the Rhizobium strains F75, H45, IC59 and IC76.",
